{"title":"","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":" ","toc":false},"headingText":"VIOLIN 🎻:","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n\nBeen playing since I was seven years old! Formerly, I was the concertmaster of the [Michigan Pops Orchestra](https://www.michiganpops.org/) from 2023-2025. My favorite piece of orchestral music is [Sibelius' Symphony No. 2](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rVzJDgDnKLI).\n\n## DANCING 💃:\n\nI was trained as a rhythmic gynmast growing up *(think ribbons, twirling, and tosses....and less Simone Biles tumbling across the floor...)*.\n\nIn college, as I transitioned to contemporary and jazz dancing, I've had to pleasure of choreographing two pieces:\n\n::: {.columns style=\"gap: 30px;\"}\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n{{< video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j1LCCAfRAYk&pp=ygUTcHVyZSBkYW5jZSBkb2cgZGF5cw%3D%3D >}}\n:::\n\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n{{< video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IfrJup29FCg >}}\n:::\n:::\n\n## RUNNING 🏃‍♀️:\n\nWork in progress! And I couldn't have done it without the [Nike Run Club](https://www.nike.com/nrc-app).\nI've run a couple of 5Ks in the past, and formally trained for the Ann Arbor Trinity Health Probility 10K in October 2025. Now, my sights are set of the Detroit Half-Marathon in October 2026!","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n## VIOLIN 🎻:\n\nBeen playing since I was seven years old! Formerly, I was the concertmaster of the [Michigan Pops Orchestra](https://www.michiganpops.org/) from 2023-2025. My favorite piece of orchestral music is [Sibelius' Symphony No. 2](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rVzJDgDnKLI).\n\n## DANCING 💃:\n\nI was trained as a rhythmic gynmast growing up *(think ribbons, twirling, and tosses....and less Simone Biles tumbling across the floor...)*.\n\nIn college, as I transitioned to contemporary and jazz dancing, I've had to pleasure of choreographing two pieces:\n\n::: {.columns style=\"gap: 30px;\"}\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n{{< video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j1LCCAfRAYk&pp=ygUTcHVyZSBkYW5jZSBkb2cgZGF5cw%3D%3D >}}\n:::\n\n::: {.column width=\"50%\"}\n{{< video https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IfrJup29FCg >}}\n:::\n:::\n\n## RUNNING 🏃‍♀️:\n\nWork in progress! And I couldn't have done it without the [Nike Run Club](https://www.nike.com/nrc-app).\nI've run a couple of 5Ks in the past, and formally trained for the Ann Arbor Trinity Health Probility 10K in October 2025. Now, my sights are set of the Detroit Half-Marathon in October 2026!"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","css":["styles.css"],"toc":false,"output-file":"Interests.html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Format